{"tid":1161874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔好再講］十幾歲冇做過乜冇做過乜！","createTime":"2019-05-19T13:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T12:48:43.000Z","uid":199559,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80297ac4c97362ef1e33eba7666482b3216c2b3e","tid":1161874,"uid":199559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"你知唔知道真係好令一個人自卑<br />\n<br />\n比啲同理心 將心比心<br />\n我見好多人都因為討論區而改變咗自己既價值觀<br />\n<br />\n我寧願世界翻到冇網絡既時候<br />\n人人都會純啲<br />\n<br />\n隔離個po笑人十幾歲都冇搭過飛機<br />\n你可能派膠好開心<br />\n<br />\n但係人地細個屋企窮可能無得選擇<br />\n做人比啲尊重啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"a0736568dccaf2806071839127cfd83bd8537154","tid":1161874,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"我十幾歲時冇同女同學日屌夜屌<br />\n<br />\n好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02295eea8f2b8e12f37536e3b30e1ca0f49343e","tid":1161874,"uid":199559,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0736568dccaf2806071839127cfd83bd8537154","tid":1161874,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"我十幾歲時冇同女同學日屌夜屌<br />\n<br />\n好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"珍惜你依家有既<br />\n屌西唔應該佔據你人生重要既位置"},{"pid":"56a8dffee57acca2eaa3ed8e23cedfcd67553cef","tid":1161874,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e02295eea8f2b8e12f37536e3b30e1ca0f49343e","tid":1161874,"uid":199559,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a0736568dccaf2806071839127cfd83bd8537154","tid":1161874,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"我十幾歲時冇同女同學日屌夜屌<br />\n<br />\n好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T15:45:44.000Z","msg":"珍惜你依家有既<br />\n屌西唔應該佔據你人生重要既位置"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"應唔應該就唔可以咁講，太主觀<br />\n<br